---
title: Target State — CRM as System of Record
---
graph TD
    subgraph CRM["CRM — System of Record"]
        C1[Customer & Account Data]
        C2[Course Catalog]
        C3[Event Courses]
        C4[Course Seats]
        C5[Course Bookings]
        C6[Qualification Categories]
        C7[Exams]
        C8[Automation Engine]
    end

    subgraph INT["Integration Layer\nCeligo / Zapier"]
        I1[Event Routing]
        I2[State Change Sync]
    end

    subgraph EC["eCommerce Platform\n(Consumer)"]
        E1[Course Listings]
        E2[Inventory — synced from CRM]
        E3[Purchases → webhook out]
    end

    subgraph LMS["LMS — Delivery Only\n(Consumer)"]
        L1[Content Delivery]
        L2[Completions → event out]
    end

    subgraph COMMS["Automated Communications\n(Zero-touch)"]
        CO1[Enrollment Confirmations]
        CO2[Post-Program Documentation]
        CO3[Weekly Resource Rosters]
        CO4[Cancellation Notices]
    end

    CRM -->|State change events| INT
    INT -->|Sync listings, inventory, cancellations| EC
    EC -->|Purchase webhook| INT
    INT -->|Create Course Seat| CRM
    LMS -->|Completion event| CRM
    C8 -->|Record state triggers| COMMS

    style CRM fill:#d4edda,stroke:#28a745,color:#000
